---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 記事一覧
description: 宇宙・海事の制度解説記事の一覧です。
pagination:
  data: collections.articles
  size: 20
  alias: posts
permalink: "/articles/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page/{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}"
---
<div class="wrap">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>記事一覧</h1>
    <p>全 {{ collections.articles | length }} 件</p>
  </header>
  <div class="page-body">
    <ul class="card-list cols-3">
      {% for a in posts %}
      {% include "partials/article-card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% if pagination.pages.length > 1 %}
    <nav class="pagination" aria-label="ページ送り">
      {% for pageUrl in pagination.hrefs %}
      {% if page.url == pageUrl %}<span aria-current="page">{{ loop.index }}</span>
      {% else %}<a href="{{ pageUrl }}">{{ loop.index }}</a>{% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </nav>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>
